{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WELCOME TO DEMONOPHOBIA COMPANY!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Demonophobia Company is a RPG + Visual Novel game that shows 'Angel of glory, Gloria' experiences after she disguises herself as 'Demon of vanity, Burbary' and joined the company.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Synopsis</strong></i>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>'Angel of glory, Gloria' got a mission to disguise as 'Demon of vanity, Burbary' and joined 'Demonophobia Company' to find the hell's significant secrets, since hell's atmosphere will be much relaxed due to the big festival.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Burbary tried to pretend like a normal demon, however, she met 'red eyes' and fainted. Seven Deadly Sins department's manager 'Teressa' says that she will help Burbary, but the strange demon 'Fey' also joins as an unexpected guest...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">    </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help Burbary and find this company's top secrets!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make attractive demon friends! (Or you don't have to.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy 9 amounts of endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find 30 achievements that are included in-game! (10 of them are hidden!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finally, wait for your show :)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nobody will blame about your choices.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>How to control</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Arrow keys - move</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spacebar - OK</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ESC - Menu open / cancel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SHIFT - run</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">CTRL - Skip dialog</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">F5 - Reset game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* Demonophobia Compa